Citadel to Sign Investment Deal for Transport Unit, Alam Reports

-- B y   A h m e d   A .   N a m a t a l l a
-- 
2011-06-27T07:40:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/citadel-to-sign-investment-deal-for-transport-unit-alam-reports.html
The  European Investment Bank  and
 Germany ’s  DEG  will direct $21 million into a Citadel Capital SAE
fund that controls the private-equity firm’s unit in charge of
environment-friendly transportation,  Al Alam Al Youm  reported,
without saying where it got the information.  Citadel will sign the investment agreement on June 29, the
Cairo-based newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ahmed A Namatalla in Cairo at 
 anamatalla@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  